description: Ninth powers ending nontrivially in a nonzero ninth power.
comments: Many of the initial elements match elements of A017289. However, 1002^9 is in this sequence but not in A017289, so the sequences are not the same. - _David W. Wilson_, May 24 2008
example: Numbers of the form (10*k+1)^9, k>=1, are in the list and end in 1=1^9.The number 1002^9=1018...004512 is in the list and ends in 512=2^9.
author: _David W. Wilson_
